HEADWORD: Agnize
<hw>Ag*nize"</hw> <pr>(⟦acr⟧g*n⟦imac⟧z")</pr>, <pos>v. t.</pos>
<ety>[Formed like <ets>recognize</ets>, fr. L.
<ets>agnoscere</ets>.]</ety> <def>To recognize; to acknowledge.</def>
<mark>[Archaic]</mark>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>I do <qex>agnize</qex> a natural and prompt alacrity.</q>
<rj><qau>Shak.</qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Agnoiology</ent>⟦br⟧
